description:
Luis J. Gomez and Big Jay Oakerson are comics and podcasters. Together, they host “Story Warz” and “Legion of Skanks” with Dave Smith. Luis also hosts “Real Ass Podcast” with Zac Amico, and Big Jay hosts “The Bonfire” on SiriusXM with Robert Kelly. Big Jay’s two-part crowdwork special, “Them/They,” is available on YouTube and vinyl, and Luis’s new special, “You’re Making This Worse,” premieres on YouTube on November 2.
